0to%20fight%20him%20off.%20The%20man%20stabbed%20Mr%20Khan%20six%20times%2C%20causing%20injuries%20to%20his%20left%20hand%20and%20neck%20and%20leaving%20a%20knife%20lodged%20in%20his%20spine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20intruder%20was%20asked%20what%20he%20wanted%2C%20he%20allegedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsaif-ali-khans-attacker-demanded-rs-1-crore-at-his-house-7488346%5C%22%3Edemanded%20Rs%201%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Two%20house%20helps%20were%20also%20injured%20in%20the%20attack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Out%20Of%20Danger'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaif%20Ali%20Khan%20was%20rushed%20to%20the%20Lilavati%20Hospital%20by%20his%20son%2C%20Ibrahim%2C%20and%20doctors%20said%20he%20is%20stable%20and%20out%20of%20danger.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BMr%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20was%20admitted%20to%20the%20hospital%20around%202%20am%20with%20alleged%20history%20of%20assault%20by%20some%20unknown%20person.%20He%20sustained%20severe%20injuries%20to%20the%20thoracic%20spinal%20cord%20due%20to%20a%20lodged%20knife%20in%20the%20spine.%20Emergency%20surgery%20was%20performed%20to%20remove%20the%20knife%20and%20repair%20leaking%20spinal%20fluid.%20Two%20other%20deep%20wounds%20on%20his%20left%20hand%20and%20one%20other%20on%20his%20neck%20were%20repaired%20by%20the%20plastic%20surgery%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20Nitin%20Dange%20of%20Lilavati%20Hospital%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20happy%20to%20confirm%20that%20Mr.%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20is%20completely%20stable%20now.%20He%20is%20recovering%20well%20and%20out%20of%20danger%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20attack%20under%20sections%20of%20robbery%2C%20trespassing%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bgrievous%20hurt%20caused%20while%20committing%20lurking%20house-trespass%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20eight%20teams%20have%20been%20formed%20to%20investigate%20t