n's%20economy%2C%20economists%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESpain's%20plan%20to%20impose%20a%20100%25%20tax%20on%20homebuyers%20from%20non-EU%20countries%20like%20the%20US%20and%20UK%20may%20fail%20to%20achieve%20its%20intended%20results%2C%20and%20could%20easily%20backfire%20on%20the%20country's%20economy%2C%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Pedro%20S%C3%A1nchez%20announced%20the%20measure%20on%20Monday%2C%20as%20part%20of%20his%20government's%20efforts%20to%20tackle%20the%20country's%20growing%20housing%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20approved%20by%20lawmakers%2C%20the%20100%25%20tax%20would%20effectively%20double%20the%20cost%20of%20properties%20for%20non-EU%20homebuyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ES%C3%A1nchez%20said%20that%20too%20many%20foreign%20buyers%20saw%20Spanish%20property%20as%20an%20investment%2C%20and%20were%20buying%20homes%20for%20financial%20gains%20rather%20than%20to%20live%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20experts%20said%20the%20impact%20may%20not%20be%20what%20the%20government%20hoped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJes%C3%BAs%20Alonso%2C%20a%20real-estate%20agent%20with%20Engel%20%26amp%3B%20V%C3%B6lkers%2C%20said%20the%20tax%20was%20unlikely%20to%20resolve%20Spain's%20housing%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20he%20said%20it%20could%20trigger%20a%20decline%20in%20demand%20for%20luxury%20properties%2C%20which%20could%20reduce%20new%20projects%2C%20especially%20in%20regions%20reliant%20on%20foreign%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20the%20move%20could%20hurt%20regions%20reliant%20on%20foreign%20spending%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20retail%20and%20hospitality%20sectors%2C%20especially%20in%20coastal%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20drop%20in%20demand%20could%20discourage%20new%20developments%20and%20stagnate%20this%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Spain's%20Association%20of%20Registrars%2C%20foreigners%20bought%2024%2C700%20properties%20in%20Spain%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%202024%2C%20accounting%20for%2015%25%20of%20all%20real%20estate%20purchases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20included%20EU%20and%20non-EU%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20was%20higher%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%202024%2C%20when%20foreigners%20bought%20and%20sold%2069%2C412%20properties%2C%20or%2020.4%25%20of%20total%20sales%20and%20purchases%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.notariado.org%2Fliferay%2Fc%2Fdocument_library%2Fget_file%3Fuuid%3D8ea3a639-45b6-40be-ac8f-b2f0cc79d572%26groupId%3D2289837%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Spain's%20General%20Council%20of%20Notaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Fatas%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20economics%20at%20INSEAD%2C%20a%20French%20business%20school%2C%20said%20foreign%20purchases%20are%20not%20large%20enough%20to%20determine%20market%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20described%20the%20100%25%20tax%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Beasy%26quot%3B%20fix%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomplex%26quot%3B%20problem%2C%20one%20that%20ignores%20the%20underlying%20cause%20of%20Spain's%20housing%20crisis%2C%20which%20is%20about%20supply%20and%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20research%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caixabankresearch.com%2Fen%2Fsectoral-analysis%2Freal-estate%2Fstrong-demand-and-short-supply-shape-spains-real-estate-sector%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECaixa%20Bank%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20supply%20of%20new%20housing%20in%20Spain%20is%20being%20weighed%20down%20by%20factors%20including%20a%20lack%20of%20land%20earmarked%20for%20development%20and%20a%20shortage%20of%20skilled%20labor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20the%20housing%20supply%20in%20the%20coming%20years%2C%20the%20gap%20between%20supply%20and%20demand%20will%20steadily%20widen%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECaixa%20Bank%20said%20in%20September%20that%20it%20expected%20Spanish%20house%20prices%20to%20rise%20by%205%25%20in%202024%2C%20and%202.8%25%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJos%C3%A9%20Carlos%20D%C3%ADez%20Gangas%2C%20an%20associate%20partner%20at%20the%20venture%20capital%20firm%20LUAfund%2C%20said%20the%20government's%20strategy%20is%20to%20try%20to%20curb%20demand%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20echoing%20Fatas'%20point%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20shortage%20of%20supply%2C%20and%20the%20greatest%20effect%20will%20be%20on%20prices%2C%20which%20will%20surely%20continue%20to%20rise%20until%20more%20houses%20come%20on%20the%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Spain%20has%20seen%20many%20ghost%20towns%20spring%20up%2C%20due%20in%20part%20to%20the%202008%20financial%20crisis%2C%20a%20lack%20of%20public%20services%2C%20and%20migration%20from%20rural%20areas%20to%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mariscal-abogados.com%2Fwhy-invest-in-abandoned-villages-in-spain%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThere%2520are%2520more%2520than%25203.000%2Cin%2520Andalusia%252C%2520Aragon%2520and%2520Catalonia.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESome%20estimates%3C%2Fa%3E%20point%20to%20upward%20of%203%2C000%20abandoned%20villages%2C%20even%20as%20other%20areas%20struggle%20to%20find%20enough%20housing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20experts%20say%20the%20latest%20government%20idea%20could%20backfire%20on%20the%20economy%20as%20a%20whole.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDoes%20it%20make%20sense%20to%20make%20it%20difficult%20for%20a%20foreigner%20to%20buy%20a%20home%20in%20Spain%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20Fatas%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BClearly%2C%20this%20represents%20a%20flow%20of%20capital%20into%20Spain%20that%20can%20have%20positive%20effects%20on%20the%20economy.%26quot%3B%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EHe%20said%20that%20stopping%20these%20flows%20would%20%26quot%3Bnegatively%20affect%20the%20construction%2C%20tourism%20sector%2C%20and%20anyone%20who%20could%20benefit%20from%20such%20a%20transaction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20articl