ose%20to%20the%20project%20said%20Season%202%20had%20%E2%80%9Cceased%20production.%E2%80%9D%20Variety%20understands%20that%20the%20show%2C%20which%20was%20around%20three%20months%20into%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22K.J.%20Yossman%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2025%2Ftv%2Fglobal%2Fnoel-fielding-adventures-of-dick-turpin-season-2-ceased-production-1236275674%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20To%20Build%20Bigger%2C%20Better%203rd%20Rocket%20Launch%20Pad%20Ahead%20Of%20100th%20Liftoff%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20an%20eye%20on%20sending%20an%20Indian%20on%20the%20Moon%2C%20the%20Union%20cabinet%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20given%20permission%20to%20build%20a%20massive%20launch%20pad%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20Sriharikota.%20The%20Union%20cabinet%20today%20in%20a%20standalone%20decision%20cleared%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20third%20launch%20pad%20at%20the%20Satish%20Dhawan%20Space%20Centre%20(SDSC)%20in%20Sriharikota.%20This%20will%20be%20the%20launch%20pad%20from%20where%20an%20Indian%20could%20be%20sent%20in%20a%20rocket%20to%20land%20on%20the%20Moon%20by%202040.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spindle-shaped%20island%20of%20Sriharikota%2C%20some%20100%20km%20north%20of%20Chennai%20on%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20coast%2C%20already%20has%20two%20launch%20pads.%20The%20third%20launch%20pad%20will%20be%20ready%20in%20four%20years%20and%20will%20cost%20Rs%203%2C984%20crore%20to%20build.%20It%20will%20accommodate%20India's%20'monster%20rocket'%2C%20the%20Next%20Generation%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(NGLV).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESriharikota%20is%20also%20host%20to%20India's%20first%20private%20launch%20pad%20made%20by%20Agnikul%20Cosmos%20Pvt%20Ltd%2C%20from%20which%20a%20rocket%20named%20Agnibaan%20Sorted%20was%20launched%20on%20May%2030%2C%202024%20for%20a%20sub-orbital%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGLV%20stands%20nearly%2090%20metres%20-%20taller%20than%20the%20Qutab%20Minar%20-%20and%20will%20have%20three%20times%20the%20present%20payload%20capability%20with%201.5%20times%20the%20cost%20compared%20to%20LVM3.%20It%20will%20have%20reusability%2C%20resulting%20in%20low-cost%20access%20to%20space%20and%20modular%20green%20propulsion%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20has%20allocated%20Rs%208%2C239%20crore%20to%20develop%20the%20NGLV%2C%20which%20will%20be%20completed%20in%2096%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20goals%20of%20the%20Indian%20space%20programme%20need%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20human-rated%20launch%20vehicles%20with%20high%20payload%20capability%20and%20reusability.%20Hence%2C%20the%20development%20of%20the%20NGLV%20has%20been%20taken%20up%20to%20carry%20a%20maximum%20payload%20of%2030%20tonnes%20to%20low-Earth%20orbit%20with%20a%20reusable%20first%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20achieved%20self-reliance%20in%20space%20transportation%20systems%20to%20launch%20satellites%20up%20to%2010%20tonnes%20to%20low-Earth%20orbit%20and%204%20tonnes%20to%20geo-synchronous%20transfer%20orbit%20through%20the%20currently%20operational%20launch%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETill%20date%2C%20Sriharikota%20has%20seen%2099%20significant%20launches%20and%20the%20next%20liftoff%20of%20the%20Geo-Synchronous%20Launch%20Vehicle%20Mark-2%20will%20be%20the%20100th%20launch%20of%20a%20new-generation%20navigation%20satellite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia's%20first%20launch%20pad%20is%20used%20for%20launching%20the%20Polar%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(PSLV)%20and%20the%20newer%20second%20launch%20pad%20can%20launch%20both%20PSLV%20and%20Launch%20Vehicle%20Mark-3.%20The%20third%20launch%20pad%20when%20ready%20will%20launch%20NGLV%20and%20with%20some%20upgradation%20it%20can%20also%20be%20used%20to%20send%20an%20Indian%20to%20the%20Moon%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20V%20Narayanan%2C%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20land%20pad%20is%20designed%20to%20have%20a%20configuration%20that%20is%20universal%20and%20adaptable%20to%20support%20not%20only%20the%20NGLV%2C%20but%20also%20the%20LVM3%20vehicles%20with%20semi-cryogenic%20stage%20as%20well%20as%20scaled-up%20configurations%20of%20NGLV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20realised%20with%20a%20maximum%20industry%20participation%20by%20fully%20using%20ISRO's%20experience%20in%20establishing%20the%20earlier%20launch%20pads%20and%20maximally%20sharing%20the%20existing%20launch%20complex%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20today%2C%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Transportation%20Systems%20are%20completely%20reliant%20on%20two%20launch%20pads%20i.e.%20the%20first%20launch%20pad%20and%20the%20second%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20one%20was%20realised%2030%20years%20ago%20for%20the%20PSLV%20and%20continues%20to%20provide%20launch%20support%20for%20the%20PSLV%20and%20the%20SSLV.%20The%20second%20launch%20pad%20was%20established%20primarily%20for%20the%20GSLV%20and%20the%20LVM3%2C%20and%20also%20functions%20as%20a%20standby%20for%20PSLV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20launch%20pad%20has%20been%20operational%20for%20almost%2020%20years%20and%20has%20enhanced%20the%20launch%20capacity%20towards%20enabling%20some%20commercial%20missions%20of%20PSLV%2FLVM3%20along%20with%20the%20national%20missions%20including%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission.%20The%20second%20one%20is%20now%20getting%20ready%20to%20launch%20the%20human-rated%20LVM3%20for%20the%20Gaganyaan%20missions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20expanded%20vision%20of%20the%20Indian%20space%20programme%20during%20the%20'Amrit%20Kaal'%20including%20the%20Bharatiya%20Antariksh%20Station%20(BAS)%20by%202035%20and%20an%20Indian-crewed%20lunar%20landing%20by%202040%20need%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20heavier%20launch%20vehicles%20with%20new%20propulsion%20systems%2C%20which%20cannot%20be%20met%20by%20the%20existing%20launch%20pads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20expeditious%20establishment%20of%20a%20third%20launch%20pad%20to%20cater%20to%20a%20heavier%20class%20of%20next-generation%20launch%20vehicles%20and%20as%20a%20stand%20by%20for%20the%20second%20launch%20pad%20is%20highly%20essential%20so%20as%20to%20meet%20the%20evolving%20space%20transportation%20requirements%20for%20another%2025-30%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20making%20a%20second%20launch%20port%20at%20Kulasekarapattinam%2C%20a%20coastal%20village%20in%20Thoothukudi%20district%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20The%20facility%20is%20being%20constructed%20over%202%2C350%20acres.%20This%20is%20being%20designed%20to%20launch%20small%20rockets%20such%20as%20the%20Small%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(SSLV)%20and%20smaller%20rockets%20made%20by%20India's%20private%20companies.%20PM%20Modi%20laid%20the%20foundation%20stone%20on%20February%2028%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737031080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fdodo8hb8_sriharikota_625x300_16_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-to-build-bigger-better-3rd-rocket-launch-pad-in-andhra-pradesh-sriharikota-ahead-of-100th-liftoff-7488138%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20an%20eye%20on%20sending%20an%20Indian%20on%20the%20Moon%2C%20the%20Union%20cabinet%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20given%20permission%20to%20build%20a%20massive%20launch%20pad%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20Sriharikota.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-to-build-bigger-better-3rd-rocket-launch-pad-in-andhra-pradesh-sriharikota-ahead-of-100th-liftoff-7488138%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pope%20Francis%20falls%20at%20Santa%20Marta%20house%2C%20hurts%20his%20arm%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737030982000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117302176%2Cimgsize-475016