caption%3EAn%20Arizona%20justice%20committee%20has%20recommended%20that%20KPMG%20receive%20a%20unique%20state%20license%20allowing%20it%20to%20practice%20law.%3Cp%3ECharles%20Platiau%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20law%20market%20is%20largely%20off-bounds%20to%20Big%20Four%20firms%20due%20to%20ethical%20rules%20on%20legal%20independence.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKPMG%20is%20close%20to%20changing%20that%20by%20securing%20a%20unique%20license%20in%20Arizona%20to%20practice%20law.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETraditional%20law%20firms%20shouldn't%20feel%20threatened%20by%20the%20move%2C%20a%20legal%20expert%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EKPMG%20is%20one%20step%20closer%20to%20becoming%20the%20first%20Big%20Four%20firm%20to%20set%20up%20a%20legal%20division%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20an%20Arizona%20judicial%20committee%20unanimously%20recommended%20that%20the%20state%20Supreme%20Court%20approve%20KPMG%20US's%20application%20for%20a%20unique%20state%20license%20that%20would%20allow%20it%20to%20practice%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20approved%2C%20the%20firm%20will%20establish%20KPMG%20Law%20US%20as%20an%20alternative%20business%20structure%20(ABS).%20The%20Arizona%20Supreme%20Court%20told%20BI%20it%20would%20weigh%20the%20decision%20on%20January%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArizona%20began%20its%20ABS%20program%20in%202021%2C%20scrapping%20a%20rule%20that%20prevents%20non-legal%20ownership%20of%20law%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rule%20was%20set%20by%20the%20American%20Bar%20Association%20and%20only%20allows%20licensed%20lawyers%20to%20own%20or%20invest%20in%20law%20firms%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20prevent%20conflicting%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20held%20back%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-four-deloitte-pwc-kpmg-ey-staff-revenues-focus-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBig%20Four%20professional%20services%20firms%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20KPMG%2C%20Deloitte%2C%20EY%2C%20and%20PwC%20%E2%80%94%20from%20establishing%20legal%20divisions%20in%20the%20US%20as%20they%20have%20done%20in%20other%20key%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPracticing%20law%20in%20the%20US%20%26quot%3Bis%20something%20that%20no%20Big%20Four%20network%20firm%20can%20currently%20do%2C%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EChristian%20Athanasoulas%2C%20a%20partner%20in%20KPMG's%20Tax%20Division%20and%20US%20head%20of%20Tax%20services%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20does%20provide%20business%20advice%20to%20legal%20clients%20in%20the%20US%2C%20he%20explained%2C%20but%20does%20%26quot%3Bnot%20interpret%20and%20apply%20legal%20standards%20to%20legal%20questions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAthanasoulas%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-impact-billable-hour-lawyers-legal-world-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvances%20in%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20growing%20demand%20for%20alternative%20legal%20services%20made%20it%20the%20right%20time%20to%20establish%20KPMG%20Law%20US%2C%20and%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bexcited%20by%20the%20opportunity%26quot%3B%20that%20Arizona's%20regulatory%20reform%20presented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPending%20approval%2C%20this%20innovation%20would%20differentiate%20KPMG%20Law%20US%20both%20in%20the%20legal%20and%20the%20consulting%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227628%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22KPMG%20building%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6788e58250dfd88e193eb26a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224898%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKPMG%20Law%20already%20provides%20legal%20services%20in%20more%20than%2080%20jurisdictions%20globally.%3Cp%3ESch%C3%B6ning%2Fullstein%20bild%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20aims%20to%20focus%20primarily%20on%20large-scale%2C%20process-driven%20work%2C%20such%20as%20volume%20contracting%2C%20remediation%20exercises%2C%20and%20M%26amp%3BA-driven%20harmonization%20of%20contracts.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKPMG%20will%20position%20itself%20as%20complementing%20the%20services%20of%20traditional%20law%20firms%20rather%20than%20competing%20with%20them.%20It%20won't%20work%20on%20complex%20commercial%20transactions%2C%20trademark%20disputes%2C%20and%20other%20areas%20that%20are%20%26quot%3Bcore%20capabilities%20of%20traditional%20law%20firms%2C%26quot%3B%20Athanasoulas%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20they%20do%20have%20over%20competitors%20is%20the%20ability%20to%20harness%20KPMG's%20holistic%2C%20global%20suite%20of%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20see%20opportunities%20in%20the%20market%20to%20provide%20these%20required%20tasks%2C%20at%20scale%2C%20with%20better%20controls%20and%20more%20standardized%20outcomes%20than%20some%20existing%20market%20participants%20currently%20provide%2C%26quot%3B%20Athanasoulas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20work%20would%20not%20be%20limited%20to%20Arizona%20but%20could%20extend%20nationally%2C%20depending%20on%20individual%20state%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKPMG%20is%20already%20a%20major%20player%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flatham-watkins-us-law-firm-poaching-top-uk-lawyers-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglobal%20legal%20landscape%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20providing%20legal%20services%20in%20more%20than%2080%20jurisdictions.%20In%20the%20last%20financial%20year%2C%20the%20tax%20%26amp%3B%20legal%20division%20was%20KPMG's%20fastest-growing%20function%2C%20expanding%20by%20almost%2010%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222348241b-cc59-42ac-bc28-8443c4a42ca4%5C%22%3EThe%20Big%20Four%20and%20the%20US%20legal%20landscape%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pending%20approval%20of%20KPMG%20Law%20US's%20ABS%20status%20raises%20questions%20about%20whether%20the%20other%20leading%20firms%20will%20follow%20suit%20and%20whether%20that%20will%20change%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20US%20legal%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Arizona%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20it%20introduced%20the%20ABS%20program%20to%20%26quot%3Btransform%20the%20public's%20access%20to%20legal%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%202020%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.azcourts.gov%2FPortals%2F201%2FPress%2520Releases%2F2020Releases%2F082720RulesAgenda.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20rules%20stand%20in%20the%20way%20of%20making%20those%20services%20available%2C%20the%20rules%20should%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20100%20firms%20have%20since%20been%20approved%20to%20practice%20law%20under%20the%20program.%20Advocates%20for%20the%20Arizona%20ABS%20program%20say%20it%20deepens%20competition%2C%20lowers%20prices%2C%20and%20facilitates%20easier%20access%20to%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUtah%20is%20running%20a%20similar%20pilot%20program%2C%20and%20there%20are%20exceptions%20in%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%2C%20that%20allow%20non-lawyers%20to%20hold%20minority%20stakes%20in%20a%20law%20firm.%20But%20other%20states%20have%20not%20yet%20followed%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20frequently%20stated%20concerns%20are%20that%20non-lawyer%20ownership%20or%20investment%20will%20create%20conflicts%20or%20low-quality%20work%20because%20of%20profit%20motivations%2C%26quot%3B%20Brad%20Blickstein%2C%20CEO%20of%20Blickstein%20Group%2C%20a%20legal%20industry%20consultancy%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKPMG%20said%20any%20new%20firm%20would%20be%20governed%20by%20the%20same%20high%20ethical%20standards%20that%20apply%20to%20other%20law%20firms%2C%20and%20there%20would%20be%20no%20crossover%20between%20legal%20services%20clients%20and%20audit%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELegal%20experts%20have%20been%20predicting%20that%20the%20Big%20Four%20will%20move%20into%20the%20US%20law%20market%20for%20several%20years%2C%20Blickstein%20said.%20While%20they%20may%20take%20some%20work%20over%20time%2C%20traditional%20law%20firms%20shouldn't%20feel%20threatened%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKPMG%20is%20somewhat%20limited%20in%20what%20it%20can%20do%20as%20an%20Arizona%20law%20firm%2C%20and%20even%20in%20markets%20like%20the%20UK%20where%20they%20have%20free%20rein%2C%20the%20Big%20Four%20has%20not%20put%20too%20many%20law%20firms%20out%20of%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20continue%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20Big%20Four%20will%20eventually%20have%20a%20meaningful%20-%20but%20not%20existential%20-%20impact%20on%20US%20law%20firms%20and%20legal%20departments%2C%26quot%3B%20Blickstein%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20step%20in%20that%20direction%2C%20but%20only%20a%20step.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpmg-law-us-arizona-application-big-four-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737029386000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678787f6e294a7514e8d2580%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpmg-law-us-arizona-application-big-four-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Big%20Four%20giant%20is%20using%20a%20unique%20regulatory%20rule%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Arizona%20to%20build%20a%20first-of-its-kind%20legal%20practise.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pthompson%40insider.com%20(Polly%20Thompson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpmg-law-us-arizona-application-big-four-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20this%20married%20woman%20used%20ChatGPT%20to%20create%20the%20perfect%20boyfriend%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737029327000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117301293%2Cimgsize-54986.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fhow-this-ma