%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Husband%20and%20wife%20preparing%20dinner%20in%20the%20kitchen%20with%20mother-in-law.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6787d9548951662c9f204e35%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224494%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20(not%20pictured)%20is%20considering%20asking%20his%20mother-in-law%20to%20move%20in%20with%20his%20family.%3Cp%3E10'000%20Hours%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20wife%20and%20I%20are%20considering%20asking%20my%20mother-in-law%20to%20move%20in%20with%20us.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere%20are%20plenty%20of%20benefits%20to%20multigenerational%20households.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20have%20room%20in%20our%20home%20for%20her%2C%20it's%20good%20for%20our%20budget%2C%20and%20we%20love%20spending%20time%20with%20her.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20mother-in-law%20was%20recently%20widowed.%20Although%20she%20is%20independent%2C%20in%20good%20health%2C%20and%20has%20her%20own%20home%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20are%20considering%20having%20her%20move%20in%20with%20us.%20This%20way%20of%20living%2C%20with%20multiple%20generations%20of%20a%20family%20under%20one%20roof%2C%20is%20known%20as%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flive-in-multigenerational-home-crowded-special-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eintergenerational%20households%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%26quot%3B%20And%20it%20can%20offer%20some%20valuable%20benefits.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI'm%20in%20favor%20of%20intergenerational%20households%20for%20many%20reasons%20%E2%80%94%20and%20why%20my%20family%20might%20try%20this%20at%20home.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220a6971ff-e169-4a62-9074-47f83b8e4774%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20countries%20do%20it%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-living-with-parents-multigenerational-households-financial-benefits-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIntergenerational%20households%20are%20common%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20many%20other%20countries.%20Research%20from%20the%20UN%20shows%20that%20as%20of%202019%2C%20in%2067%20out%20of%20100%20countries%20that%20had%20data%20available%2C%20older%20people%20tend%20to%20live%20with%20their%20extended%20families%20instead%20of%20alone.%20When%20I%20lived%20in%20Japan%2C%20I%20remember%20seeing%20how%20common%20it%20was%20for%20young%20adults%20to%20keep%20living%20at%20home%20with%20their%20parents%20well%20into%20their%2030s%20or%20beyond.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELiving%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliving-multigenerational-home-lessons-pateince-openness-death-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emultiple%20generations%20under%20one%20roof%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20a%20great%20way%20for%20families%20to%20stay%20connected%20and%20for%20young%20people%20to%20save%20on%20rent%20while%20starting%20their%20careers.%20This%20way%20of%20living%20is%20not%20so%20rare%20in%20America%2C%20either.%20Pew%20Research%20shows%20that%20as%20of%202021%2C%20about%2018%25%20of%20the%20US%20population%20resided%20in%20multigenerational%20households.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20not%20always%20easy%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flessons-learned-living-with-my-jewish-grandparents-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eshare%20a%20home%20with%20a%20grandparent%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20your%20parents%3B%20sometimes%2C%20people%20want%20to%20get%20out%20from%20under%20their%20parents'%20roof%20or%20have%20more%20privacy.%20But%20sometimes%2C%20sharing%20living%20space%20with%20older%20family%20members%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%20and%20keep%20your%20family%20connected%20a