g%20to%20reporters%20on%20Thursday%20afternoon%20after%20attending%20a%20special%20screening%20of%20the%20movie%20%3Cem%3E'Emergency'%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20starring%20Kangana%20Ranaut%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAmong%20all%20the%20megacities%20in%20the%20country%2C%20Mumbai%20is%20the%20safest.%20It%20is%20true%20that%20some%20incidents%20take%20place%20sometimes%20and%20they%20should%20be%20treated%20with%20seriousness%20but%20to%20say%2C%20based%20on%20one%20incident%2C%20that%20Mumbai%20is%20unsafe%20would%20not%20be%20correct.%20This%20tarnishes%20Mumbai's%20image.%20But%20the%20government%20is%20working%20to%20make%20Mumbai%20even%20safer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20early%20morning%20burglary%20attempt%20at%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan's%20home%20in%20Bandra%2C%20during%20which%20the%20actor%20was%20stabbed%20six%20times%20but%20is%20out%20of%20danger%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%20leader%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%20was%20among%20the%20first%20to%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20government%2C%20asking%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20celebrities%20are%20not%20safe%2C%20who%20in%20Mumbai%20is%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20a%20shame%20that%20Mumbai%20sees%20another%20high-profile%20attempt%20on%20life%2C%20the%20attack%20on%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20yet%20again%20raises%20questions%20on%20Mumbai%20Police%20and%20the%20Home%20Minister.%20This%20is%20after%20a%20series%20of%20incidents%20that%20show%20there%20is%20a%20deliberate%20attempt%20to%20undermine%20Mumbai%20by%20targeting%20big%20names%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MP%20also%20brought%20up%20the%20murder%20of%20former%20Maharashtra%20minister%20Baba%20Siddique%20in%20October%20last%20year%20and%20the%20firing%20outside%20actor%20Salman%20Khan's%20home%20in%20April.%20Both%20of%20these%20incidents%20had%20also%20taken%20place%20in%20Bandra%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20Mumbai's%20poshest%20areas%20and%20is%20home%20to%20many%20of%20the%20city's%20rich%20and%20famous.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'In%20A%20Shambles'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20relief%20that%20Mr%20Khan%20is%20stable%2C%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20and%20son%20of%20former%20chief%20minister%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20said%20the%20incident%20highlights%20the%20poor%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20under%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20intrusion%20and%20knife%20attack%20on%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20is%20shocking.%3Cbr%3E%5CnWe%20are%20relieved%20to%20hear%20that%20he%20is%20stable%20and%20recovering%2C%20and%20we%20pray%20that%20tough%20times%20are%20over%2C%20and%20he%20bounces%20back%20to%20normalcy%20at%20the%20earliest.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20fact%20that%20it%20happened%2C%20however%2C%20only%20highlights%20the%20absolute%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%20(%40AUThackeray)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAUThackeray%2Fstatus%2F1879814329417248820%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2016%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20murder%20of%20a%20sarpanch%20in%20Beed%20-%20allegedly%20involving%20the%20close%20aide%20of%20a%20leader%20from%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20led-NCP%20-%20and%20a%20custodial%20death%20in%20Parbhani%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20wrote%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20it%20(the%20attack%20on%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan)%20happened%2C%20however%2C%20only%20highlights%20the%20absolute%20shambles%20law%20%26amp%3B%20order%20is%20in%20Maharashtra.%20Over%20the%20past%203%20years%2C%20hit-and-run%20cases%2C%20actors%20and%20politicians%20being%20threatened%20and%20cases%20like%20those%20in%20Beed%20and%20Parbhani%20only%20show%20that%20the%20Government%20has%20been%20an%20absolute%20failure%20in%20curbing%20crime%20and%20maintaining%20law%20and%20order.%20Do%20we%20have%20anyone%20in%20the%20government%20that%20cares%20about%20citizen%20safety%20at%20all%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilar%20statements%20were%20made%20by%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20leader%20Clyde%20Castro%2C%20Varsha%20Gaikwad%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20Sanjay%20Raut%20from%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttacking%20the%20BJP%20over%20the%20issue%2C%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20said%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3BThis%20morning%20we%20got%20the%20shocking%20news%20that%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20was%20stabbed...%20I%20pray%20that%20he%20gets%20well%20soon%20but%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%20that%20such%20a%20big%20actor%20who%20lives%20in%20such%20a%20safe%20place%20is%20attacked%20in%20his%20house%20in%20this%20manner.%20This%20raises%20questions%20on%20the%20state%20and%20central%20government%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'What%20About%20Order%3F'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20actors%20and%20others%20from%20the%20film%20fraternity%20have%20also%20spoken%20out%20after%20the%20attack.%20Actor%20and%20filmmaker%20Pooja%20Bhatt%20said%20she%20had%20%26quot%3Bnever%20felt%20so%20unsafe%20before%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20posts%20on%20X%20tagging%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Ministers%20Eknath%20Shinde%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20she%20asked%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Blawlessness%26quot%3B%20to%20be%20curbed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCan%20this%20lawlessness%20please%20be%20curbed%20%40MumbaiPolice%20%40CPMumbaiPolice.%20We%20need%20more%20Police%20presence%20in%20Bandra.%20The%20city%20and%20especially%20the%20queen%20of%20the%20subburbs%2C%20have%20never%20felt%20so%20unsafe%20before%20(sic)%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Bhatt%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20post%2C%20she%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BLaw%20%26amp%3B%20Order.%20We%20have%20laws..%20what%20