for%20the%20Opposition%20also.%20They%20tried%20to%20outsource%20politics%2C%20they%20tried%20to%20use%20international%20organisations%20instead%20of%20relying%20on%20our%20own%20agencies%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20investigative%20organisations...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20critical%20questions%20have%20been%20raised%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Mr%20Anderson's%20announcement.%20Does%20Hindenburg's%20disbanding%20prove%20the%20shoot%20and%20scoot%20nature%20of%20the%20organisation%3F%20What%20does%20it%20say%20about%20those%20who%20believe%20in%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%3F%20Was%20it%20a%20conspiracy%20of%20the%20deep%20state%20and%20foreign%20elements%3F%20Can%20Hindenburg%20still%20be%20punished%3F%20Or%20was%20it%20a%20big%20foreign%20interference%20in%20the%20'India%20Story'%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajya%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20senior%20lawyer%20Mahesh%20Jethmalani%20alleged%20Hindenburg's%20disbanding%20signals%20deeper%20implications%2C%20suggesting%20possible%20scrutiny%20by%20the%20US%20authorities%20or%20fear%20of%20investigation%20for%20its%20role%20in%20targeting%20Adani%20Group%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jethmalani%20linked%20the%20development%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bdemocratic%20deep-state%26quot%3B%20led%20by%20billionaire%20George%20Soros%2C%20terming%20it%20an%20act%20of%20%26quot%3Beconomic%20terrorism%26quot%3B%20aimed%20at%20destabilising%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEither%20he%20has%20already%20been%20sounded%20out%20by%20investigating%20authorities%20in%20the%20US%20or%20he%20fears%20that%20he%20will%20be%20investigated%20for%20his%20role%20in%20the%20attempt%20to%20shake%20India's%20economy%20by%20bare%20hammering%20of%20Adani%20shares%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jethmalani%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Group%20Chairman%20Gautam%20Adani%20at%20the%20annual%20general%20meeting%20in%20June%20said%20the%20group%20%26quot%3Bfaced%20baseless%20accusations%20made%20by%20a%20foreign%20short%20seller%20that