ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc62737zqn68o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Trump's%20Return%20Has%20Exposed%20Europe's%20Weaknesses%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEurope%20had%20experienced%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20heat%20from%20Donald%20Trump%20during%20his%20first%20term%20as%20president.%20He%20had%20cast%20doubt%20on%20the%20continuing%20relevance%20of%20NATO%2C%20viewed%20it%20as%20a%20financial%20burden%20on%20the%20US%20because%20the%20Europeans%20were%20not%20spending%20enough%20on%20their%20own%20defence%2C%20and%20demanded%20that%20they%20spend%202%25%20of%20their%20GDP%20on%20defence.%20He%20showed%20his%20disdain%20towards%20the%20EU%20by%20supporting%20Brexit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20belief%20that%20Russia%20had%20interfered%20in%20the%20US%20presidential%20election%20in%20Trump's%20favour%20had%20created%20misgivings%20that%20he%20might%20pursue%20a%20more%20flexible%20policy%20towards%20Moscow%20over%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict.%20His%20right-wing%2C%20nationalistic%20political%20orientation%20clashed%20with%20Europe's%20left-leaning%20liberalism.%20His%20Make%20America%20Great%20Again%20(MAGA)%20slogan%20created%20anxiety%20as%20it%20was%20considered%20inward-looking%2C%20protectionist%20and%20tending%20towards%20isolationism.%20European%20politicians%20were%20concluding%20that%20Europe%20and%20Trump's%20America%20no%20longer%20shared%20the%20same%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20Europe%20Cope%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20now%20come%20back%20to%20power%20with%20a%20thumping%20majority.%20The%20Republicans%20have%20also%20won%20control%20of%20both%20houses%20of%20the%20US%20Congress.%20Trump%20is%20undoubtedly%20convinced%20that%20his%20re-election%2C%20despite%20all%20the%20legal%20and%20other%20efforts%20of%20the%20Democrats%20to%20disqualify%20and%20prevent%20him%20from%20fighting%20the%20election%2C%20has%20vindicated%20his%20proclaimed%20domestic%20and%20foreign%20policy%20agendas.%20Europe%20and%20others%20will%20have%20to%20cope%20with%20the%20unpredictability%2C%20impetuousness%20and%20self-assertion%20of%20this%20maverick%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20even%20before%20his%20inauguration%2C%20has%20put%20Europe%20under%20stress%20by%20his%20power%20play%20in%20questioning%20the%20continent's%20territorial%20integrity%20by%20laying%20claim%20to%20Greenland.%20During%20his%20first%20term%2C%20too%2C%20he%20had%20laid%20his%20eyes%20on%20Greenland%2C%20but%20this%20time%20%2Che%20is%20brazen%20about%20acquiring%20it%20on%20grounds%20of%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20security%E2%80%9D%20and%20access%20to%20its%20natural%20resources%20such%20as%20oil%2C%20gas%2C%20lithium%20etc.%20Trump%20has%20threatened%20to%20pursue%20his%20claim%20with%20economic%20coercion%20or%20use%20of%20force%2C%20if%20necessary%2C%20as%20he%20considers%20ownership%20of%20Greenland%20an%20%E2%80%9Cabsolute%20necessity%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president-elect%20clearly%20wants%20the%20US%20to%20become%20a%20major%20Arctic%20power%20in%20anticipation%20of%20the%20melting%20of%20the%20Arctic%20ice%2C%20which%20would%20open%20up%20a%20vital%20trade%20route%20between%20Europe%2FAsia%20and%20the%20Americas%20and%20allow%20mining%20of%20the%20oceans'%20rich%20resources%20of%20oil%2C%20gas%20and%20other%20minerals%20as%20well.%20At%20present%2C%20Russia%20dominates%20the%20Arctic%20geographically%2C%20and%20China%20is%20eyeing%20it%20too%20for%20its%20potential%20for%20trade%20connectivity.%20This%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20ruthless%20great%20power%20politics%20of%20the%2019th%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20attack%20on%20Europe's%20territorial%20integrity%20puts%20Europe%20against%20the%20wall.%20Its%20dependence%20on%20the%20US%20for%20its%20security%20provides%20it%20no%20real%20option%20to%20resist.%20The%20response%20of%20European%20leaders%20has%20been%20to%20temporise%20and%20avoid%20challenging%20Trump%20head-on.%20The%20Danish%20prime%20minister%20recognises%20America's%20%E2%80%9Csecurity%20concerns%E2%80%9D%2C%20while%20also%20stating%20that%20Greenland%20is%20not%20up%20for%20sale.%20The%20US%20already%20has%20a%20military%20base%20in%20Greenland%2C%20which%20can%20be%20expanded%2C%20and%20hence%2C%20the%20argument%20of%20security%20concerns%20seems%20debatable.%20The%20autonomous%20Greenland%20government%20has%20made%20hedging%20statements.%20The%20German%20Chancellor%20has%20resorted%20to%20a%20non-specific%20statement%20to%20the%20effect%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinviolability%20of%20borders%20applies%20to%20all%E2%80%9D.%20The%20French%20foreign%20minister%20has%20avoided%20mentioning%20the%20US%20by%20name%20while%20remarking%20that%20the%20EU%20would%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20let%20other%20nations%20of%20the%20world%20attack%20its%20sovereign%20borders%2C%20whoever%20they%20are%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELost%20For%20Answers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20European%20Commission%20has%20refused%20to%20%E2%80%9Cgo%20into%20the%20specifics%E2%80%9D%20when%20asked%20to%20comment%20on%20Trump's%20claims.%20Van%20der%20Leyen%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20European%20Commission%20and%20Antonia%20Costa%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20European%20Council%2C%20stated%20evasively%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CEU%20will%20always%20protect%20our%20citizens%20and%20the%20integrity%20of%20our%20democracies%20and%20freedoms%E2%80%9D%20and%2C%20rather%20pointlessly%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20look%20forward%20to%20a%20positive%20engagement%20with%20the%20incoming%20US%20administration%2C%20based%20on%20our%20common%20values%20and%20shared%20interests.%20In%20a%20rough%20world%2C%20Europe%20and%20the%20US%20are%20stronger%20together%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEurope%20is%20embarrassed%20and%20does%20not%20quite%20know%20how%20to%20respond%20adequately.%20Its%20geopolitical%20weakness%20has%20been%20exposed%2C%20diminishing%20its%20status%20as%20a%20collective%20power.%20It%20sees%20itself%20threatened%20by%20Russian%20power%20from%20the%20East%20and%20now%20by%20American%20power%20from%20the%20West%E2%80%94one%20an%20enemy%20and%20the%20other%20an%20ally.%20In%20Russia's%20case%E2%80%94which%20is%20unlike%20that%20of%20the%20US%20seeking%20to%20seize%20Greenland%E2%80%94it%20is%20not%20a%20territory%20belonging%20to%20an%20EU%20state%20that%20is%20being%20annexed%20or%20under%20threat%20of%20annexation.%20The%20message%20from%20all%20this%20is%20that%20Europe%20is%20unable%20to%20look%20after%20its%20own%20security.%20It%20depends%20on%20US-led%20NATO%20for%20protection%2C%20but%20it%20is%20the%20leader%20of%20NATO%20that%20is%20weakening%20NATO%20solidarity%2C%20with%20an%20uncomfortable%20message%20that%20Trump's%20America%20sees%20Europe%20as%20quasi-dispensable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Double%20Bind%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20quandary%20for%20Europe%20is%20that%20if%20it%20were%20to%20react%20strongly%20and%20decide%20to%20condemn%20the%20US%20territorial%20bid%2C%20it%20would%20need%20an%20internal%20consensus%2C%20and%20seeking%20one%20could%20divide%20NATO.%20The%20NATO%20edifice%2C%20which%20is%20considered%20vital%20for%20Europe's%20security%20by%20member%20states%2C%20especially%20in%20East%20and%20Central%20Europe%2C%20could%20well%20begin%20to%20crack%2C%20given%20Trump's%20known%20disdain%20for%20the%20transatlantic%20alliance.%20A%20strong%20anti-US%20reaction%20could%20also%20weaken%20Europe%20politically%20against%20Russia.%20Europe's%20no-holds-barred%20discourse%20against%20Russia%20for%20seeking%20to%20annex%20the%20territory%20of%20a%20sovereign%20state%20and%20allegedly%20altering%20the%20map%20of%20Europe%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20the%20Second%20World%20War%2C%20as%20against%20a%20compliant%20attitude%20towards%20the%20US%20for%20a%20somewhat%20similar%20goal%2C%20could%20well%20become%20unsustainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEurope's%20problem%20is%20that%20it%20cannot%20build%20its%20security%20simply%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20countries%20increasing%20their%20defence%20budgets%20individually.%20The%20smaller%20European%20countries%E2%80%94and%20there%20are%20many%E2%80%94increasing%20their%20defence%20budgets%20means%20little.%20To%20be%20autonomously%20secure%2C%20Europe%20needs%20to%20rely%20on%20its%20own%20arms%20industry%2C%20European%20countries%20to%20buy%20European-produced%20arms%2C%20and%20Europe%20to%20have%20some%20kind%20of%20a%20centralised%20European%20chain%20of%20command.%20This%20will%20require%20a%20deepening%20of%20the%20EU%20as%20a%20sovereign%20entity%2C%20on%20which%20there%20is%20no%20political%20consensus%20amongst%20Europeans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20things%20are%2C%20European%20security%20has%20remained%20frozen%20in%20the%20Cold%20War%20matrix%2C%20with%20Russia%20being%20an%20enduring%20threat%20and%20the%20US%20standing%20as%20a%20bulwark%20against%20it.%20Although%20France%20and%20the%20UK%20are%20nuclear%20powers%2C%20their%20nuclear%20umbrellas%20are%20not%20politically%20acceptable%20to%20many%20European%20countries.%20They%20would%20prefer%20to%20rely%20only%20on%20the%20US%20nuclear%20umbrella%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20face%20of%20Russia's%20formidable%20nuclear%20arsenal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENarrative%20Wars%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEuropean%20public%20opinion%20could%20get%20confused%20if%20tensions%20between%20the%20EU%20and%20the%20US%20over%20the%20Greenland%20issue%20become%20acrimonious%2C%20and%20could%20well%20begin%20to%20affect%20public%20attitudes%20towards%20Russia%2C%20with%20mounting%20support%20for%20some%20compromise%20with%20Russia%20over%20Ukraine%20instead%20of%20a%20complete%20refusal%20to%20engage%20in%20a%20dialogue%20with%20Moscow.%20The%20discourse%2C%20in%20some%20circles%2C%20could%20well%20turn%20into%20one%20of%20US%20imperialism%20versus%20Russian%20imperialism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Ukraine%20issue%2C%20Trump's%20repeated%20declarations%20on%20engaging%20in%20a%20dialogue%20with%20Russia%20to%20find%20a%20solution%2C%20the%20statement%20by%20the%20incoming%20US%20National%20Security%20Adviser%20that%20Russia%20cannot%20be%20expelled%20from%20all%20the%20territory%20it%20holds%2C%20and%20the%20implied%20message%20that%20Ukraine%20will%20have%20to%20yield%20territory%2C%20as%20well%20as%20talk%20of%20arranging%20a%20Trump-Putin%20meeting%2C%20are%20huge%20political%20blows%20to%20Europe%2C%20whose%20leadership%20has%20persistently%20demonised%20Russia%20and%20Putin%20and%20closed%20doors%20to%20any%20dialogue%20with%20Moscow.%20Trump%20is%20upending%20Europe's%20position%20of%20complete%20alignment%20with%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20position%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict.%20There%20is%20reported%20concern%20in%20Brussels%20that%20Trump%20may%20lift%20some%20sanctions%20on%20Russia%20as%20part%20of%20a%20potential%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20security%20issues%2C%20Trump's%20presidency%20could%20increase%20economic%20pressures%20on%20the%20EU.%20This%20will%20come%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20economic%20costs%20paid%20by%20the%20EU%20because%20of%20Ukraine-related%20economic%20sanctions%20on%20Russia.%20During%20his%20first%20term%2C%20Trump%20had%20targeted%20Germany%20for%20its%20mercantilist%20trade%20policies.%20Germany's%20current%20economic%20woes%20add%20to%20Europe's%20vulnerability%20to%20US%20economic%20pressures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EClash%20Of%20Values%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20personal%20deep%20antipathy%20to%20%E2%80%98wokeism'%2C%20DEI%20(Diversity%2C%20Equity%2C%20and%20Inclusion)%20and%20gender%20identity%20issues%20will%20be%20another%20clash%20of%20%E2%80%9Cvalues%E2%80%9D%20with%20Europe.%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20who%20is%20amplifying%20many%20of%20Trump's%20political%20and%20social%20views%2C%20has%20already%20become%20a%20major%20headache%20for%20the%20European%20political%20class.%20He%20is%20openly%20interfering%20in%20European%20politics%20by%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20supporting%20the%20right-wing%20nationalist%20party%20(AfD)%20in%20Germany%2C%20and%20the%20right-wing%20Reform%20Party%20in%20the%20UK.%20He%20has%20brutally%20targeted%20prime%20minister%20Keith%20Starmer%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgrooming%20gangs%E2%80%9D%20scandal%2C%20calling%20him%20%E2%80%9Ccomplicit%20in%20the%20rape%20of%20Britain%E2%80%9D.%20Vice-president-elect%20J.D.Vance%20has%20also%20attacked%20the%20UK%20over%20not%20suppressing%20Islamism%20in%20the%20country.%20Trump%20Jr%20has%20joined%20in%20criticising%20the%20Labour%20Party%20too.%20This%20bodes%20ill%20for%20the%20US-UK%20special%20relationship.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnAll%20in%20all%2C%20Europe's%20dependence%20on%20the%20US%20and%20its%20limited%20margin%20of%20manoeuvre%20have%20been%20brutally%20exposed%20with%20Trump's%20coming%20ascension%20to%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Kanwal%20Sibal%20was%20Foreign%20Secretary%20and%20Ambassador%20to%20Turkey%2C%20Egypt%2C%20France%20and%20Russia%2C%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Of%20Mission%20in%20Washington.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737019260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fr92i04ro_donald-trump_625x300_07_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ftrumps-return-has-exposed-europes-weaknesses-7486560%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Europes%20dependence%20on%20the%20US%20and%20its%20limited%20margin%20of%20manoeuvre%20have%20been%20brutally%20exposed%20with%20Trumps%20coming%20ascension%20to%20the%20White%20House.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ftrumps-return-has-exposed-europes-weaknesses-7486560%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BGambhir%20Went%20Out%20With...%26quot%3B%3A%20BCCI's%20Decision%20To%20Curb%20Wives'%20Stay%20Explained%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20has%20already%20proposed%20some%20stricter%20rules%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20recent%20results%20the%20team%20has%20incurred.%20The%20stay%20of%20players'%20wives%2C%20including%20names%20like%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Anushka%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F117930-anushka-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAnushka%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ritika%20Sajdeh%2C%20Athiya%20Shetty%2C%20etc.%20will%20be%20limited%20to%20just%202%20weeks%20on%2045-day%20long%20tours.%20While%20the%20new%20rules%20have%20yet%20to%20be%20fully%20implemented%2C%20a%20report%20has%20explained%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20Indian%20board's%20contemplation%20of%20such%20an%20action.%20The%20changes%20are%20being%20thought%20of%20purely%20because%20of%20what%20the%20BCCI%20management%20noticed%20Down%20Under%20during%20India's%20tour%20of%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fafter-debacle-down-under-bcci-may-cap-stay-of-wives%2Farticleshow%2F117251471.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20claimed%20that%20Indian%20players%20were%20spotted%20travelling%20in%20groups%20during%20the%20Australia%20tour%2C%20with%20the%20desired%20team%20bonding%20missing.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20report%20further%20claimed%20that%20only%20one%20team%20dinner%20during%20the%20Australia%20tour%20saw%20the%20entire%20group%20of%20players%20being%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20board%20is%20a%20bit%20concerned%20that%20a%20team%20that%20has%20been%20so%20consistent%20across%20formats%20for%20more%20than%20half%20a%20decade%20is%20suddenly%20struggling%20to%20click%20with%20almost%20the%20same%20set%20of%20players.%20It%20comes%20down%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20galvanising%20force%20in%20the%20team.%20It%20has%20emerged%20that%20players%20are%20consumed%20in%20their%20individual%20lives%20once%20they%20are%20done%20with%20training%20or%20a%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20BCCI%20source%20told%20TOI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlayers%20these%20days%20have%20their%20families%20around%20along%20with%20a%20big%20entourage.%20Some%20have%20even%20requested%20to%20stay%20in%20different%20hotels%20and%20a%20few%20have%20made%20their%20own%20travel%20arrangements%20within%20the%20country.%20These%20players%20are%20barely%20seen%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20team.%20The%20board%20is%20contemplating%20restricting%20the%20length%20of%20stay%20for%20families%20to%20two%20weeks%20on%20a%20lengthy%20tour%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20has%20also%20claimed%20that%20no%20celebratory%20team%20dinner%20was%20witnessed%20after%20Team%20India%20won%20the%20series%20opener%20in%20Perth.%20Even%20head%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Gambhir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F563-gautam-gambhir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGautam%20Gambhir%3C%2Fa%3E%20went%20with%20his%20own%20people%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20squad%20was%20divided%20into%20different%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20expected%20the%20team%20to%20have%20a%20customary%20celebratory%20team%20dinner%20after%20India%20won%20the%20first%20Test%20in%20Perth.%20Instead%2C%20everyone%20in%20the%20squad%20went%20out%20in%20groups.%20Gambhir%20went%20out%20with%20his%20own%20people.%20There%20was%20only%20one%20team%20dinner%20during%20the%20two-month%20tour.%20Previous%20team%20management%20used%20to%20organize%20outdoor%20activities%20with%20the%20entire%20team.%20It%20helps%20in%20building%20team%20spirit%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20seeing%20the%20team%20divided%20into%20groups%2C%20head%20coach%20Gambhir%20even%20t