iduals%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20basic%20necessities%2C%20like%20toothbrushes%2C%20but%20now%20they%20have%20the%20means%20to%20buy%20what%20they%20need.%20Some%20had%20been%20separated%20from%20their%20families%20for%20years%20and%20lacked%20the%20resources%20to%20reunite.%20After%20joining%20us%2C%20they%20were%20able%20to%20visit%20their%20loved%20ones%20with%20the%20money%20they%20saved.%20For%20instance%2C%20one%20uncle%2C%20who%20started%20working%20with%20us%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20has%20already%20earned%20over%20Rs%201%20lakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20the%20young%20founder%2C%20while%20discussing%20the%20impact%20of%20his%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20underprivileged%20students%2C%20like%20Naisha%20Mungilwar%2C%20the%20bags%20were%20more%20than%20just%20an%20aid%20for%20school%20supplies.%20They%20represented%20hope.%20A%20student%20from%20Prashant%20Vidyalaya%20in%20Nagpur%2C%20she%20comes%20from%20a%20family%20where%20survival%20is%20a%20constant%20struggle.%20Her%20father%20works%20as%20a%20labourer%20and%20her%20mother%20is%20a%20maid%20who%20barely%20manages%20to%20feed%20Naisha%20and%20her%20younger%20brother.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20school%20on%20most%20days%20during%20the%20monsoon%20season%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20receiving%20the%20bag%20from%20Threads4Good%2C%20I%20started%20attending%20school%20regularly.%20I%20can%20carry%20my%20books%20safely%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F371220%2Fias-jitendra-jorwal-transforms-lives-of-underprivileged-children-women-in-rural-punjab-through-education-health-projects%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emid-day%20meals%3C%2Fa%3E%20organised%20by%20the%20team%20helps%20me%20focus%20better%20in%20class.%20Thanks%20to%20this%2C%20I%20passed%20my%20Class%2010%20with%20flying%20colours%20and%20now%20aim%20to%20become%20a%20doctor.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5C