0from%20Guwahati%2C%20and%20interning%20at%20a%20pharmaceutical%20company%20in%20Bengaluru.%20In%20Mao%2C%20where%20job%20security%20and%20a%20stable%20career%20were%20prioritised%2C%20her%20decision%20to%20pursue%20floriculture%20was%20met%20with%20concern.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20told%20my%20parents%20about%20my%20plan%20to%20work%20with%20flowers%2C%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20very%20convinced.%20Even%20my%20neighbours%20questioned%20me%2C%20asking%20when%20I%20would%20go%20back%20to%20the%20city%20and%20get%20a%20%E2%80%98proper%E2%80%99%20job%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chokhone%20admits.%20But%20despite%20the%20odds%2C%20she%20stayed%20the%20course%2C%20even%20when%20the%20rest%20of%20her%20community%20remained%20sceptical.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20worked%20with%20flowers%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20connecting%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333343%2Ffarmer-producer-organisations-fpos-small-farmers-bayer-increase-yield-profits-jardalu-mango%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmall-scale%20farmers%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20Mao%20with%20urban%20markets%20began%20to%20take%20root.%20Farmers%20in%20the%20region%20were%20facing%20significant%20challenges%2C%20including%20limited%20market%20access%20and%20low%20returns%20on%20their%20produce.%20Flowers%2C%20however%2C%20presented%20a%20promising%20alternative.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20idea%20behind%20Dianthe%20was%20simple%20yet%20powerful%3A%20to%20create%20a%20market%20for%20local%20farmers%E2%80%99%20flowers%2C%20help%20them%20generate%20better%20revenue%2C%20and%20connect%20them%20with%20consumers%20in%20larger%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Chokhone