zon-1735581755-600x450.jpeg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-29-at-9.05.49-PM-1_11zon-1735581755-400x300.jpeg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-29-at-9.05.49-PM-1_11zon-1735581755-200x150.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-29-at-9.05.49-PM-1_11zon-1735581755-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-393889%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDianthe%20employs%2050-60%20farmers%2C%20with%20numbers%20fluctuating%20based%20on%20demand%20and%20order%20volume%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20people%20were%20doubtful.%20They%20had%20always%20grown%20vegetables%2C%20and%20flowers%20seemed%20like%20an%20uncertain%20choice.%20But%20when%20they%20saw%20the%20flowers%20bloom%2C%20they%20realised%20they%20could%20sell%20them%20for%20three%20to%20four%20times%20the%20price%20of%20vegetables%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20Dianthe%2C%20Chokhone%20makes%20multiple%20products%20like%20candles%2C%20wedding%20gifting%20items%2C%20flower%20arrangements%2C%20bouquets%2C%20boutonni%C3%A8res%2C%20and%20epoxy%20flower%20presentations%20along%20with%20working%20with%20B2B%20brands.%20Chokhone%20and%20her%20team%20are%20always%20experimenting%20with%20different%20types%20of%20flowers%20to%20expand%20their%20range%20and%20cater%20to%20diverse%20market%20demands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20food%20colouring%20is%20commonly%20used%20for%20dyeing%20flowers%2C%20which%20is%20a%20standard%20industry%20practice.%20However%2C%20Dianthe%20is%20also%20exploring%20the%20use%20of%20natural%20dyes%20extracted%20from%20vegetables%20and%20fruits%2C%20although%20this%20option%20remains%20limited%20in%20scope.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20growing%20network%20of%20empowered%20farmers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDianthe%E2%80%99s%20success%20has%20been%20rooted%20in%20its%20ability%20to%20provide%20a%20platform%20for%20farmers%20to%20connect%20with%20buyers%2C%20while%20also%20educating%20them%20on%20best%20practices%20for%20floriculture.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20the%20farmers%20here%20were%20working%20with%20limited%20land%20and%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20But%20once%20they%20started%20growing%20flowers%2C%20they%20could%20earn%20multiple%20times%20more%20than%20they%20ever%20did%20with%20vegetables%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chokhone%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20efforts%20also%20include%20training%20farmers%20on%20how%20to%20properly%20care%20for%20flowers%2C%20ensuring%20that%20they%20meet%20market%20demands.%20%E2%80%9CFlowers%20need%20to%20be%20harvested%20at%20the%20right%20time%2C%20and%20they%20must%20be%20handled%20delicately.%20We%20teach%20the%20farmers%20how%20to%20do%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20exciting%20aspects%20of%20Dianthe%E2%80%99s%20growth%20has%20been%20its%20ability%20to%20empower%20women%20in%20Mao.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20have%20always%20been%20a%20significant%20part%20of%20the%20agricultural%20workforce%2C%20and%20many%20of%20them%20have%20embraced%20floriculture%20as%20a%20way%20to%20supplement%20their%20income.%20Chokhone%E2%80%99s%20work%20has%20created%20jobs%20a