D%20Esther%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CEither%20that%20or%20the%20produce%20rot%20and%20they%20are%20left%20with%20nothing.%20The%20risk%20was%20high%2C%20which%20is%20why%20less%20people%20would%20venture%20into%20floriculture%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlowers%20are%20mostly%20aesthetic%20and%20require%20specific%20care%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20they%20bloom%20at%20the%20right%20time%20and%20maintain%20their%20quality%20for%20market%20demand.%20Since%20last%20year%2C%20Chokhone%20has%20been%20providing%20training%20to%20farmers%20interested%20in%20these%20details.%20Some%20of%20these%20tips%20include%20using%20wiring%20and%20support%20systems%20to%20create%20specific%20shapes%2C%20ensuring%20that%20flowers%20meet%20the%20standards%20expected%20by%20urban%20buyers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20despite%20operating%20in%20a%20relatively%20isolated%20region%2C%20Chokhone%20is%20working%20towards%20building%20market%20linkages%2C%20connecting%20with%20different%20artisans%20and%20sectors%20to%20increase%20awareness%20of%20their%20project%20and%20explore%20potential%20collaborations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20beautiful%20albeit%20difficult%20terrain%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20and%20running%20a%20floriculture%20business%20in%20a%20remote%20area%20like%20Mao%20is%20not%20without%20its%20challenges.%20Connectivity%20issues%2C%20lack%20of%20skilled%20labour%2C%20and%20limited%20resources%20have%20all%20made%20the%20journey%20difficult.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShipping%20flowers%20is%20a%20challenge.%20Sometimes%20they%20rot%20during%20transit%2C%20and%20the%20delivery%20services%20here%20don%E2%80%99t%20always%20take%20care%20of%20the%20products%20properly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chokhone%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.th